{"tid":1841150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"根本唔只係醫護要罷工，大家準備好初五唔啟市未？","createTime":"2020-01-25T07:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T17:26:45.000Z","uid":38071,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f22e9f618a87bdd5f3cd5d03b18efd8b807fe86b","tid":1841150,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:17:45.000Z","msg":"你點知隔離個同事喺新年做咗啲咩<br />\n你又點知你拜年無舐到嘢（當然最理想就係留喺屋企唔去拜年。我今年就謝絕曬所有拜年啦，尤其係去過中國嘅人。）<br />\n<br />\n為咗自己為咗香港為咗唔好加重醫護人員負擔，有得home office就home office，無嘅話至少等兩個禮拜先好返工。"},{"pid":"de88d431a7c06d8150200dc7e234fda979efa069","tid":1841150,"uid":38071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:18:04.000Z","msg":"我就最怕死嘅，香港政府一日唔封關我一日都唔敢出街。返工同條命相比我揀我條命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b04273177adb322c26550ad29f840fe55a7d3a","tid":1841150,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef9263dbb1bf668254db320c24ef221c26ae314","tid":1841150,"uid":38071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:22:15.000Z","msg":"有無人都打算同老細要求home office<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c457c7c46afe5ac25fd6a0edf19432a85f39f40","tid":1841150,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:25:46.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n日日淨係識叫醫護罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844ba31480f20a18057392c23e3fdc6632e43dd0","tid":1841150,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c457c7c46afe5ac25fd6a0edf19432a85f39f40","tid":1841150,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:25:46.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n日日淨係識叫醫護罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:42:23.000Z","msg":"全港一齊罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個個都咁驚社區爆發，就唔好一邊驚一邊又出門口去返工呀"},{"pid":"f122b621359b6555c5b66b744c5c18098cd42993","tid":1841150,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:42:57.000Z","msg":"希望大家都可以怕死啲一齊唔出街"},{"pid":"9241b0a8beadd52a65fc38489d2eb1d23aeb1250","tid":1841150,"uid":71253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ef9263dbb1bf668254db320c24ef221c26ae314","tid":1841150,"uid":38071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:22:15.000Z","msg":"有無人都打算同老細要求home office<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:43:34.000Z","msg":"連更都唔報了<br />\n唔封關就唔會出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n工可以再搵，命就得一條"},{"pid":"d947db236c9cafaff70584c19862a24a449d8dab","tid":1841150,"uid":329324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:45:09.000Z","msg":"不如停工停課啦 咁樣係唔店架"},{"pid":"d48a0ee7038e6b1970a1d6f67a9985f269946936","tid":1841150,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"844ba31480f20a18057392c23e3fdc6632e43dd0","tid":1841150,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c457c7c46afe5ac25fd6a0edf19432a85f39f40","tid":1841150,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:25:46.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n日日淨係識叫醫護罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:42:23.000Z","msg":"全港一齊罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個個都咁驚社區爆發，就唔好一邊驚一邊又出門口去返工呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:45:43.000Z","msg":"班人淨係識屌醫護唔罷工<br />\n做入境同司機個d就cup印比支那人入黎車佢地出市區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正常返工返學就去被傳染<br />\n<br />\n香港人無一個是無辜的"},{"pid":"fccbeaa9ccd111038a0f82c9b347017b179883d6","tid":1841150,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:46:26.000Z","msg":"希望唔好個個都唔想出街，但又以為身邊嘅人都會返工，搞到逼住又要驚又要返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72a74a6fcb0f7a6f9804441ca5285e0fc320bba","tid":1841150,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:57:55.000Z","msg":"防疫除咗戴口罩仲有好多嘢可以做！<br />\nhome office保平安<br />\n減少去人多嘅地方 <br />\n食飯之前/ 返到屋企洗手消毒雙手<br />\n小心處理自己個口罩，唔好除低周圍擺<br />\n返屋企沖涼，唔好着出街衫攤上床<br />\n定時消毒下屋企啲地板傢俬<br />\n倒1：49落渠<br />\n早睡早起 強身健體<br />\n<br />\n呀媽係女人不過大家有無跟住做先？定仲係唔知驚，求求其其做啲唔做啲就算"},{"pid":"3fa1b440db846722285636484c88caada3844ce6","tid":1841150,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:26:45.000Z","msg":"越嚟越多人吹雞初五唔啟市了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}